{
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "chat_1",
      "provider": "chat",
      "config": {
        "hideForm": true,
        "mode": "Source",
        "parameters": {},
        "type": "chat"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 40,
          "y": 200
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_1",
      "provider": "agent_deepagent",
      "config": {
        "default": {
          "advanced_mode": false,
          "instructions": [
            "You are the Company Brain. You answer a teammate's question using ONLY the company notes provided in the message, and you TRANSLATE the answer into the asker's role so they never have to decode someone else's context.",
            "Each message has the shape: 'PERSONA: <engineer|sales>\\nQUESTION: <text>\\n\\nNOTES:\\n<markdown notes from the brain>'. Read the notes, find what is relevant to the question, and synthesize a direct answer — do not dump the notes back.",
            "Translate to the PERSONA. engineer = precise and technical: name the PRs/issues/files, what changed mechanically, status, and any follow-ups; jargon is fine. sales = customer-facing and non-technical: what it means for customers and prospects, the value/benefit, what's now possible or fixed, and a one-line you could say on a call; avoid code/jargon, never mention internal file names.",
            "Ground every claim in the notes and cite the source note titles or PR/issue numbers you used (e.g. 'PR #5', 'issue-2'). If the notes do not contain the answer, say so plainly rather than guessing. Keep it tight — a few sentences or short bullets, not an essay."
          ]
        }
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "questions",
          "from": "chat_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 280,
          "y": 200
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_1",
      "provider": "llm_openai",
      "config": {
        "profile": "openai-4o",
        "openai-4o": {
          "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_OPENAI_KEY}"
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "control": [
        {
          "classType": "llm",
          "from": "agent_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 280,
          "y": 380
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "config": {
        "laneName": "answers"
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "answers",
          "from": "agent_1"
        }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 540,
          "y": 200
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "project_id": "7e4f4119-10df-4cac-9402-75c82229f925",
  "viewport": {
    "x": 0,
    "y": 0,
    "zoom": 1
  },
  "version": 1
}